{"type":"excalidraw","version":2,"source":"excalidraw-diagram-skill","elements":[{"type":"rectangle","id":"darkbg","x":-4000,"y":-3000,"width":10000,"height":7500,"backgroundColor":"#1e1e2e","fillStyle":"solid","strokeColor":"transparent","strokeWidth":0,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"title","x":100,"y":10,"width":480,"height":30,"text":"Provider가 해결하는 3가지 문제","fontSize":22,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","fontFamily":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"rectangle","id":"r1","x":40,"y":55,"width":600,"height":55,"backgroundColor":"#1e3a5f","fillStyle":"solid","roundness":{"type":3},"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"r1_t","x":50,"y":60,"width":580,"height":45,"text":"① Prop Drilling 해결\n중간 위젯을 거치지 않고 필요한 위젯이 직접 상태를 가져옴","fontSize":14,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","fontFamily":2,"containerId":"r1","roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"rectangle","id":"r2","x":40,"y":120,"width":600,"height":55,"backgroundColor":"#2d1b69","fillStyle":"solid","roundness":{"type":3},"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"r2_t","x":50,"y":125,"width":580,"height":45,"text":"② 상태 생명주기 관리\n위젯 트리에 상태를 바인딩 → 트리에서 제거 시 자동 dispose","fontSize":14,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","fontFamily":2,"containerId":"r2","roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"rectangle","id":"r3","x":40,"y":185,"width":600,"height":55,"backgroundColor":"#1a4d2e","fillStyle":"solid","roundness":{"type":3},"strokeColor":"#22c55e","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"r3_t","x":50,"y":190,"width":580,"height":45,"text":"③ 의존성 주입 (Dependency Injection)\n위젯이 필요한 의존성을 직접 생성하지 않고 외부에서 주입받음","fontSize":14,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","fontFamily":2,"containerId":"r3","roughness":1,"opacity":100}],"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#1e1e2e"}}